{"id": 231307852, "title": "Police Kill 3 Bandits, Rescue Hostages In Katsina", "text": "The Katsina State Police Command said operatives killed three suspected bandits and rescued a number of kidnapped victims during an attack in Sabuwa local government area of the state. Spokesman of the Command, Sadiq Abubakar, in a statement made available to LEADERSHIP on Saturday, said while the operatives succeeded in foiling the kidnapping attempt, three notorious bandits were also neutralised during the encounter. \u201cOn June 7, 2024, at about 19:23 hrs, information was received at the Sabuwa Divisional Police Headquarters that armed bandits in their numbers, wielding dangerous weapons, attacked Duya Village, Maibakko Ward, Sabuwa LGA and kidnapped a number of women,\u201d Abubakar said. On receiving the report, the Divisional Police Officer (DPO), CSP Aliyu Mustapha, in collaboration with members of the vigilante, mobillised a team of operatives to the scene. The statement noted that the bandits opened fire on the security operatives team upon sighting the team, which was responded gallantly and successfully, leading to the thwarting of the kidnapping attempt. \u201cIn the course of scanning the scene, the body of three neutralised suspected bandits were recovered from the scene,\u201d it added The Commissioner of Police in the state, CP Abubakar Musa commended the operatives for their exceptional display of bravery and gallantry, reiterating the command\u2019s commitment towards ensuring the safety of the people in the state.", "summary": "The Katsina State Police Command said operatives killed three suspected bandits and rescued a number of kidnapped victims during an attack in Sabuwa local government area of the state. Spokesman of the Command, Sadiq Abubakar, in a statement made available to LEADERSHIP on Saturday, said while the operatives succeeded in foiling the kidnapping attempt, three [&#8230;]", "url": "https://leadership.ng/police-kill-3-bandits-rescue-hostages-in-katsina/", "image": "https://leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/recall-our-husbands-posted-to-niger-drama-as-police-officers-wives-protest-in-lagos-600x420-1.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-08 15:04:30", "author": "Godwin Enna", "authors": ["Godwin Enna"], "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "ng", "sentiment": 0.067}